OL,3,C'I don't want to die in hospital' -
OL,4,CFunding crisis threatens end-of-life
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"I don't know when my time runs out
OL,8,Fand therefore neither does the
OL,9,Fhospice," Marc said.
OL,11,FHe added: "The hospice can't sit there
OL,12,Fand say, 'in six months time we'll
OL,13,Fmake a bed available for Marc'. It's
OL,14,Fas and when I need it, and it might
OL,15,Fnot be there.
OL,17,F"It doesn't just scare me, it scares
OL,18,Fmy husband, it scares my family
OL,19,Fbecause I don't want to die at home
OL,20,Fand I don't want to die in a hospital."
