OL,3,C'I don't want to die in hospital' -
OL,4,CFunding crisis threatens end-of-life
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FStuart Palma, Chief Executive of The
OL,8,FSouthern Hospice Group says the sector
OL,9,Fis 'on the brink' because of a lack of
OL,10,FGovernment support.
OL,12,FThe group - which has specialist
OL,13,Ffacilities in Worthing, Hove and
OL,14,FArundel - is running at an annual loss
OL,15,Fof nearly #4m. While donations help to
OL,16,Ffund many of its services - Palma said
OL,17,Fthey only going so far.
