OL,3,C'I don't want to die in hospital' -
OL,4,CFunding crisis threatens end-of-life
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"Without any longer term commitment
OL,8,Ffrom the government for hospices, the
OL,9,Fsector will not be on the brink, it
OL,10,Fwill tip over the brink," Mr Palma
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FHe added: "Hospice care is about
OL,14,Fgiving people choice at the end of
OL,15,Flife, a choice to live well, a choice
OL,16,Fof where they wish to be and die and
OL,17,Fwith whom. If we have to reduce our
OL,18,Fservices, it means we have to restrict
OL,19,Fthat choice."
