OL,3,C'I don't want to die in hospital' -
OL,4,CFunding crisis threatens end-of-life
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FBeyond the impact on patients, Mr
OL,8,FPalma says reduced hospice care will
OL,9,Falso add pressure on the NHS.
OL,11,F"The knock-on effect is that we place
OL,12,Fa greater burden on the NHS. As
OL,13,Feveryone knows with the flu outbreak
OL,14,Frecently, the burden couldn't be
OL,15,Fhigher on the NHS as it is," he said.
OL,17,F"So that's at breaking point, and with
OL,18,Fus having to do less because of
OL,19,Ffunding, there will be an even further
OL,20,Fburden (...) But the human cost is the
OL,21,Freally devastating part of this".
