OL,3,C'I don't want to die in hospital' -
OL,4,CFunding crisis threatens end-of-life
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FHigher wage bills due to tax changes
OL,8,Fhave made palliative care more
OL,9,Fexpensive. Running Martlets, St
OL,10,FBarnabus in Worthing and Chestnut tree
OL,11,Fhouse in Sussex cost #34m last year.
OL,13,FThe Government contributed #7.5m, with
OL,14,Fthe charity needing to find the rest.
OL,16,FThe financial pressure has been
OL,17,Fexacerbated by rising demand as well,
OL,18,Fwith referrals for people aged between
OL,19,F45-65 increasing by 17% in the last
OL,20,Ftwo years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
