OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FThe Department for Health said it is
OL,8,Fturning social care around, after what
OL,9,Fit says is a 'decade of neglect'.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "We are
OL,12,Fdelivering a funding boost of more
OL,13,Fthan #4billion, reforming the Care
OL,14,FQuality Commission, improving pay and
OL,15,Fcareer opportunities for workers, and
OL,16,Fboosting domestic recruitment and
OL,17,Fretention."
